title: 이달의소녀탐구 #67 (LOONA TV #67)
summary:
It is the last filming of the day and YeoJin looks super happy.
0:10 -- Yeojin mentions that there is a puppy and it starts walking around the girls.
0:17 -- HeeJin: “It’s so cute…!”. She approaches the dog but it walks away. She names
it Kkami~.
0:10 -- HeeJin: “Kkami~ You are sitting in a funny pose.”. She approaches it again but
fails again.
